================================================================================
Scope and modifications
================================================================================

The DX7Ref C target (`Sources/DX7Ref/`) is a TEST-ONLY target. It is built
only when running `swift test` and is not linked into production builds.

Modifications applied while porting:
  - Translation from C++ to plain C
  - Flattening into a procedural API for Swift bridging
  - All public symbols namespaced with `dx7ref_` prefix
  - Header comments at the top of each file annotate provenance and
    SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0

The remainder of this repository (the `M2DXCore` Swift target — engine,
voices, tables, DSP, presets) is original work by the M2DX-Core authors,
licensed under the MIT License (see `LICENSE`). Tables and computational
kernels in the Swift target are independently generated from the
mathematical definitions of FM synthesis and the publicly documented
behavior of the DX7 hardware.

